                <p>This small trailer park got a complete makeover of all the small trailer homes with two new colors. All the homes were painted with the same concept using similar sections to give a uniformity to the design for each two tone home. For a speedy production the red accents were painted first then covered up and the final color was then sprayed followed by any touch up that were needed.</p>
